curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/9287' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2203", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2203 is a high voltage and low power  consumption linear regulator. It is capable of supplying  150mA output current. The operating input voltage is  up to 36V. The output voltage range is from 2.5V to 12V  in fixed output version.  Other features include current limit and thermal  shutdown protection.  The SGM2203 is available in Green SOT-23, SOT-23-5  and SOT-89-3 packages. It operates over an operating  temperature range of -40℃ to +85℃.  "}'
